 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=valquisssilverpalm>Valquiss Silverpalm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 148<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/14/02 2:19:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=215.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Killing halflings for faction</span><hr size=1> My opinion on this is simple.  This is a game.  A role-playing game, but still a game.<br>
<br>
Not everything is automatically acceptable simply because someone is, or even might be, role-playing.  That's just absurd.  Role-playing *Game*.  Every game has rules of reasonable conduct.  The point of soccer (football, to all you Europeans) may be to get the ball into the net, but you aren't allowed to kick the goalie in the head to do it, even if that may serve the point of the game.  There are proper ways to do things and there are improper ways to do things.  And over the top profanity lands firmly on my list of improper ways to RP.<br>
<br>
No, I can't impose this.  I don't even try, except by choosing who I will and won't RP with.  But I stand by anyone's right to say &quot;this conduct doesn't belong in my vision of this game.&quot;  And if it's something that is backed up by the rules of Norrath, I stand by their right to report it and get something done about it.  RP is not a universal excuse to do any damn thing you please, especially things that would never get accepted in any other context.  And anyone who thinks it is probably needs to sort out their issues somewhere other than in my gaming environment.<br>
<br>
Valquiss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubormwarrior.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Borm Warrior</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/14/02 2:36:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=215.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Killing halflings for faction</span><hr size=1> Valquiss, wow, thank you for putting and end to all rational discussion with your comments that effectively say &quot;End of Discussion, I have spoken.&quot; <br>
