<br>
However, while it may be difficult for you to accept, RP is also tha ability to behave in a manner different from your normal mode of response. Otherwise we have to be content with Necros that speak kindly (in acceptable RP Aulde Englishe of course) to all and gladly help little halflings with corpse retrievals. BAH. <br>
